|poter~ = ^poterono.~
..TEXT:
|quei~: The souls of Puccio Sciancato and Guercio (see notes to
vss. 148, 151).
..TEXT:
|fuggirsi~: "To run away," as souls do constantly in
this ^bolgia~ (see "ad ire...mosso," ^Inf.~ XXIV, 69).
